<p>Dave: &spades;6 &spades;7 &spades;8 &spades;9 &spades;10</p>
<p>Frankie: &clubs;2 &clubs;3 &clubs;4 &clubs;6 &clubs;7</p>
<p>Georgiana: &clubs;9 &clubs;10 &spades;J &clubs;Q &spades;K</p>
<p>Cleo: &clubs;8 &clubs;J &clubs;K &clubs;A &spades;A</p>
<p>(By Bob Stanton.)</p>
